# Ignore make / cmake build files from language stats
**/Makefile linguist-generated=true
**/makefile linguist-generated=true
**/CMakeLists.txt linguist-generated=true
**/*.cmake linguist-generated=true

# If you prefer treating them as vendored/generated:
# **/Makefile linguist-vendored=true
# **/CMakeLists.txt linguist-vendored=true
